## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="c4b8f-102">实体集级授权和验证由使用批注的方法实现 <xref:System.Data.Services.QueryInterceptorAttribute> 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c4b8f-102">Entity set-level authorization and validation is implemented by methods annotated with the <xref:System.Data.Services.QueryInterceptorAttribute>.</span></span> [!INCLUDE[ssAstoria](~/includes/ssastoria-md.md)]<span data-ttu-id="c4b8f-103">不实现安全策略，而是提供服务开发人员编写其自己的安全规则和业务验证所需的基础结构。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c4b8f-103">s do not implement security policies but instead provide the infrastructure required for service developers to write their own security rules and business validation.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="c4b8f-104">通过查询操作，可使用查询撰写来启用实体集访问控制和验证。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c4b8f-104">Entity set access control and validation is enabled through query operations by using query composition.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="c4b8f-105">若要控制基于实体的访问，请根据以下规则实现每个实体一个方法集：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c4b8f-105">To control entity-based access, implement a method-per-entity set according to the following rules:</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="c4b8f-106">此方法必须具有公共范围并使用进行批注，并将 <xref:System.Data.Services.QueryInterceptorAttribute> 实体集的名称作为参数。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c4b8f-106">The method must have public scope and be annotated with the <xref:System.Data.Services.QueryInterceptorAttribute>, taking the name of a entity set as a parameter.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="c4b8f-107">方法不能接受任何参数。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c4b8f-107">The method must accept no parameters.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="c4b8f-108">方法必须返回类型 `Expression<Func<T, bool>>` 的表达式，该表达式是要为实体集撰写的筛选器。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c4b8f-108">The method must return an expression of type `Expression<Func<T, bool>>` that is the filter to be composed for the entity set.</span></span>  
  
   
  
## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="c4b8f-109">下面的示例控制对 `Customers` 实体集的访问。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c4b8f-109">The following example controls access to the `Customers` entity set.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="c4b8f-110">每个 `Customer` 只能看到 `Orders` 与该关联的 `Customer` 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c4b8f-110">Each `Customer` can only see `Orders` associated with that `Customer`.</span></span>  
  
```  
[QueryInterceptor("Orders")]  
public Expression<Func<Order, bool>> FilterOrders()   
{  
    return o => o.Customer.Name == /* Current principal name. */;  
}   
  
// Insures that the user accessing the customer(s) has the appropriate  
// rights as defined in the QueryRules object to access the customer  
// resource(s).  
  
[QueryInterceptor ("Customers")]  
public Expression<Func<Customer, bool>> FilterCustomers()   
{  
  return c => c.Name == /* Current principal name. */ &&  
              this.CurrentDataSource.QueryRules.Contains(  
                rule => rule.Name == c.Name &&  
                        rule.CustomerAllowedToQuery == true  
              );  
}  
  
```
